    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "One fix that I see: prevent the handles to overlap. We can do it with CSS  : \n\n``` css\n.ais-range-slider--handle-lower {\n  transform: translateX(-50%);\n}\n.ais-range-slider--handle-upper {\n  transform: translateX(50%);\n}\n```\n\nWhat do you think?\n",
    "created_at": "2016-01-25T10:25:05Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/642#issuecomment-174462471",
    "id": 174462471,
