    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I believe we need to add something to our own default css file as @bobylito proposed. But we can also have a look at how http://refreshless.com/nouislider/ does it, this is the slider we use, maybe we stripped too many CSS from their original file.\n\nhttp://refreshless.com/nouislider/ do not have any issue with overlapping handles. If we find how did they do it, it would be cool\n",
