  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Well actually I just tried the first demo on the website and it does overlap. BUT the last moved handle is on the foreground, our problem is that instantsearch moves the handles programmatically making it impossible to nouislider to know which handle should be in the foreground (and so we may have handles that can't be moved because they are blocked by one another).\n\nIMHO nouislider is failing on the usability aspect by having this overlap and so we should add the CSS :)\n",
